voters' registration books were lost in November and December
last year during the registration, and some who could only reach
their legal voting age after May 29th also registered.
</P>
<P>
The biggest opposition party, the Mozambican National
Resistance Party (Renamo), has condemned the Frelimo for
fraudulent practices and asked to postpone the voting until to
June or July this year. 
