<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, March 9 (Xinhua) -- The Inter-American Development
Bank (IDB) Monday announced the approval of a 28 million U.S.
dollar loan to the Banco Hiptecario del Uruguay to help finance
the urban improvements.
</P>
<P>
