equipment for the new cultural complex of the Servicio Oficial de
Difusion Radio Television y Espectaculos (SODRE), located near the
Artigas station.
</P>
<P>
The SODRE cultural center will have facilities for musical
shows, theatrical works, film shownings, and other activities.
</P>
<P>
The investments will form part of the government's strategy to
consolidate the city's "cultural corridor," which runs from the
newly rehabilitated Artigas Station, located in the port area,
through downtown Montevideo.
</P>
<P>
The total cost of the program is 40 million dollars. In
addition to the IDB loan, local counterpart funds total 12 million
dollars. 
