report that FIFA has asked Nigeria and South Africa to bid for the
year 2006 World Cup, saying that it is willing to give the hosting
right to an African country for the first time in history.
</P>
<P>
Analysts here believe that the successful hosting of the 1999
FIFA Youth Championship will be a major boost to Nigeria's bidding
for the 2006 World Cup.
</P>
<P>
