<HEADLINE> China Has 4,000 Consultative Agencies </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 10 (Xinhua) -- China currently has more than
4,000 consultative agencies, the International Trade News
has reported.
</P>
<P>
They range from consultations for decisions, technologies and
projects to management and professions.
</P>
<P>
About half of them are located in Beijing, Shanghai, Tianjin
and Jiangsu Province, where the economies are better developed,
while central and west parts of China have only a few.
