<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 10 (Xinhua) -- Vice-Premier Li Lanqing today
urged people in the less-developed China's central and the western
parts to speed up infrastructure construction and promote economic
and social progress.
</P>
<P>
Attending a panel discussion of NPC deputies for southwestern
Guizhou Province to the Ninth National People's Congress (NPC) in
