destroyed by the navy, the paper said, adding that at least 15 Sea
Tigers in the destroyed boats were killed in the attack.
</P>
<P>
The Tamil rebels have been fighting a 15-year-old war against
the Sri Lankan government in a bid to establish a separate state
in the north and east of the country.  
