<HEADLINE> China to Spend One Billion Yuan on Marine Science </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 10 (Xinhua) -- China will spend one billion yuan
(120 million US dollars) in developing marine science and
technology before 2000, an oceanologist said here today.
